{"word":"G4401 - προχειροτονέω - procheirotonéō - prokh-i-rot-on-eh'-o - Choose before","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">προχειροτονέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">procheirotonéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">prokh-i-rot-on-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Choose before</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - முன்புநியமி"},{"paragraph":"to choose or designate beforehand"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4253 - πρό - pró - pro/4253\">G4253</a> and <a href=\"#/G5500 - χειροτονέω - cheirotonéō - khi-rot-on-eh'-o/5500\">G5500</a>; to <i>elect in advance:</i> - choose before.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}